{"tid":32343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外媒關注「中國遊客武器化」　 減少輸出遊客懲罰港台《環時》大篇幅引述","createTime":"2016-12-10T06:30:37.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T06:47:09.000Z","uid":53003,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"087555067dfed9b7ea7099553ec797fae369ab5d","tid":32343,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:30:37.000Z","msg":"環球網引述 Huffington Post&nbsp;報道，中國出現「遊客武器化 (youker weaponization)」的現象，即把遊客當做國際政治戰場上的武器。環球網大篇幅引述文章的論點，對不友善的國家和地區，中國會刻意減少輸出遊客，令他們蒙受經濟損失，香港、台灣正是其中一例。<br />\n<br />\n環時文章題為≪中國的遊客成為戰略資源　令周邊地區無可奈何≫，報道提及Huffington Post 的文章題目則為&nbsp;China On The Way To Weaponizing Youkers的文章，原刊於今日亞洲新聞。<br />\n<br />\n環球時報的文章大篇幅引述Huffington Post的文章觀點，2015 年出境中國游客接近&nbsp;1.2 億人，,預計到 2020 年將增到 2 億人次。「中國游客就是戰略資源，肯定能夠充當武器。」所以多位中國官員承認，對與中國有矛盾的國家，中國政府會私下減少游客數量。<br />\n<br />\n環時引述Huffington Post文章所指，台灣和香港的獨立及反中情緒，就導致今年 11 月，兩地大陸游客比去年各減少 30% 和 20%，似乎韓國成為中國這一戰術所針對的國家之一。由於該國部署「薩德」導彈防禦系統 (Terminal High Altitude Area Defense，THAAD)&nbsp;及與日本簽署《軍事情報保護協定》，韓中關係緊張，於是中國減少了對韓國輸出遊客。<br />\n<br />\n至於日本，報道指雖然該國現在似乎未有遊客減少跡象，但今後「可能會遭遇更大的倒霉，畢竟日本與中國的關係冰冷。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/china/%E5%A4%96%E5%AA%92%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%81%8A%E5%AE%A2%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8%E5%8C%96-%E6%B8%9B%E5%B0%91%E8%BC%B8%E5%87%BA%E9%81%8A%E5%AE%A2%E6%87%B2%E7%BD%B0%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%B0-%E7%92%B0%E6%99%82-%E5%A4%A7%E7%AF%87%E5%B9%85%E5%BC%95%E8%BF%B0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%25AA%2592%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%25B3%25A8-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%2581%258A%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E5%2599%25A8%25E5%258C%2596-%25E6%25B8%259B%25E5%25B0%2591%25E8%25BC%25B8%25E5%2587%25BA%25E9%2581%258A%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E6%2587%25B2%25E7%25BD%25B0%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258F%25B0-%25E7%2592%25B0%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%25AF%2587%25E5%25B9%2585%25E5%25BC%2595%25E8%25BF%25B0%2F&d=YHJl00JLHPb7hfT09k3P5GN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=ec398028\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%25AA%2592%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%25B3%25A8-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%2581%258A%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E5%2599%25A8%25E5%258C%2596-%25E6%25B8%259B%25E5%25B0%2591%25E8%25BC%25B8%25E5%2587%25BA%25E9%2581%258A%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E6%2587%25B2%25E7%25BD%25B0%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258F%25B0-%25E7%2592%25B0%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%25AF%2587%25E5%25B9%2585%25E5%25BC%2595%25E8%25BF%25B0%2F&h=b31f9441\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/china/%E5%A4%96%E5%AA%92%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%81%8A%E5%AE%A2%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8%E5%8C%96-%E6%B8%9B%E5%B0%91%E8%BC%B8%E5%87%BA%E9%81%8A%E5%AE%A2%E6%87%B2%E7%BD%B0%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%B0-%E7%92%B0%E6%99%82-%E5%A4%A7%E7%AF%87%E5%B9%85%E5%BC%95%E8%BF%B0/</a>"},{"pid":"c9e70da474a3bf0b6d55e85d23fa9a45ebf7f43a","tid":32343,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:34:42.000Z","msg":"快啲懲罰全世世"},{"pid":"72aae2a6aa2c1806f8fc6afaec29d2a9e212ba7f","tid":32343,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:34:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>快啲懲罰全世界</blockquote>"},{"pid":"4a9ad7c43e7d17d5afe48ec95247d5816af7377d","tid":32343,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:36:32.000Z","msg":"蝗海戰術"},{"pid":"6cbdbb48eebc188206a5fa9d03cea4f304019430","tid":32343,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:40:37.000Z","msg":"唔好以為自己咁重要先得㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你唔嚟反而我多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 寧願似未回歸仲好 ，少啲中國人仲開心 ，冇咁多假鈔電話騙案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e771566d5856d850d836d14e6b3fc7e560124b6","tid":32343,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:42:01.000Z","msg":"支那真係好撚自大， 以前未回歸沒冇乜中國人咪又係咁過 ，仲好似冇咁多麻煩嘢<img src=\"/assets